				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">You two bring up a good point, but hopefully one everyone knows:
<br />

<br />
If warrior is MT you (the casters and non-MTs) have to be more careful about aggro than if a pally or SK are. 
<br />

<br />
Zambik at 61 in a group COULD NOT steal aggro from Arslan at 60...and he tried SO hard to.  But, not all paladins are nearly as good as Arslan, so you do have to be somewhat careful.<br />_________________<br />Binnen Minder
