				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">My only argument on the DoT thing is: in a low dps situation, if I stack 5 dots on a mob, I'm IMMEDIATELY doing 500-600 dpt on the mob...hard to grab that kind of agro back.  (I've gotten dot agro from Dray, QS and a couple of other warriors if I stack them highest to lowest with no delay) If you stack your dots, lowest to highest, with a pause in between, the dpt increases at a slower rate and it allows the tank to get the agro.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://www.eq-lodestar.com/images/dark_powers.jpg"><br>Elyssia Stormbow
