<br />

<br />
i think paladins and sks working with warriors is a MARVELOUS thing. I often slap some stuns on  a mob that the warrior is tanking. why?
<br />

<br />
1. this puts me high on the agro list, if a nuke happy caster steals agro from warrior, 1 stun from me should leap frog them if i have already hit it with a stun.
<br />

<br />
2. my fast castie stuns stuns ANY mob up to lvl 65 for a good 2 seconds. that is 2 seconds that a warrior isnt getting hit <img src="images/smiles/icon_smile.gif" alt="icon_smile.gif" border="0" />
<br />

<br />
raid buffed i approach 6400 hp and 1400 ac. (with gear ive had for months and at only lvl 63). a couple more aa (once im done with SU III) and I will max out my stamina at 265 or whatever it is for lvl 63 adding even more HP and approaching the 7k mark.
<br />

<br />
i can usually take a good 5 or 6 hits, even at 800+ a pop giving the warrior (or other MT) plenty of time to get agro back. especially if there is a designated healer for "back up" tanks.
